This is a new package created to plot the Radar-Boxplot. This is a in progress work, which will soon be published.

Changelog:
1.0.0: Added parameters to tune everything in the plot.
       Removed all external dependencies except for ggplot2 suggestion.
0.2.3: Fixed documentation issues by decorating methos with @rdname radarBoxplot
0.2.2: Fixed to avoid warnings and errors while R CMD check, except for over documenting
